							},
							"branch": {
								"type": ["boolean", "string"],
								"markdownDescription": "Create branch based releases.\n\n---\n```json\n\"branch\": true\n```\n\nIf `true`, a release is created for the repositorie's default branch.\n\n---\n\n```json\n\"branch\": \"any-branch\"\n```\n\nA `string` value specifies a branch name to create releases from.",
